 your trusty mount is coming with you!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/879160/extras/9f72d8d947c6bb0b4718e179e69e0d42.webp?t=1769726883\" width=25 height=17 /></span> It’s Dangerous to Go Alone!</h2>Take on the fight alone or team up with a friend to prove your mettle. If your teammate falls in battle, find a resurrection shrine and leap back into the fray. It ain’t over ‘til it’s over!",
